Product Description

Higher cotton blend lab coats for chemistry lab students, biology lab students, pharmacists, and physicians. Made with soft and fine quality Twill fabric. Twill fabric is sanforized to control shrinkage less than 3% and mercerized for fabric strength and for a richer tone.

DR Uniforms™ lab coats contain 60% cotton and 40% polyester. The higher cotton content makes these lab coats very comfortable and gives a breathable feel to wear for long periods of time.

  • Sizes available XS - 5XL
  • 3 patch pockets
  • Side Slits to access pant pockets
  • Lead-Free buttons
  • Back Slit for easy sitting
  • Notched Lapel

From the manufacturer


DR Uniforms Lab Coat

60% Cotton / 40% Polyester Comfort Blend

Protect your clothes don’t let your clothing get dirty and stained. With this white lab coat on top of your clothes they will stay fresh and clean as long as you wear it.

  • Soft & Comfortable Fabric
  • 60/40 Cotton/Polyester Blend
  • Virtually NO Shrinkage
  • Easy to wash, instructions are provided

DR Uniforms Unisex - 60/40 Cotton/Polyester Blend Lab Coat

Student's Choice

Whether you are a medical professional, scientist, veterinarian, dental technician, pharmacist, student, just starting your career or a seasoned professional this is a lab coat you will love.

DR Uniforms have meticulously tailored Lab Coats to please customers. While remaining effortlessly comfortable, this classic lab coat will keep you looking like stylish and professional. A Simple, modern style was designed to fit the needs of anyone in need of protections from messy projects.

  • Sizes XS - 5XL
  • Full-length
  • Two front pockets, One breast pocket
  • Side Slits for accessing pant pockets
  • Back Slit for easy sitting

Easy to Wash

Our lab coats are durable and withstand many washes so they may be reused. Wrinkle resistant, lightly liquid repellant and breathable fabric make DR Uniform Lab Coats a cut above the rest.

These lab coats are designed to not restrict its wearer as least as possible and to cover them fully in order to protect them from messy projects. Breathable twill fabric for skin friendly cotton feel.

Easy to clean, machine wash with warm water, remove promptly, tumble dry. Warm Iron if needed.

Features

  • Durable Material
  • Notched lapel
  • Two front pockets, One breast pocket
  • Machine wash and dry
  • Buttons are Lead-Free
  • White Color
  • For Students and Professionals

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
